---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Father's Heart Bible™ — An Intimate Translation"
	description="An intimate translation revealing our Father's heart to a fatherless generation. Published by Spirit Media."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-stone-50 px-6 py-20 lg:py-28 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="hero-stagger">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red mb-4">Father's Heart Bible™</p>
						<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-ink-soft">
							An Intimate Translation
							<br />
							<span class="text-red">Revealing Our Father's Heart</span>
						</h1>
						<p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-stone-600 max-w-xl">For centuries, millions have read the Bible faithfully — and connected to God as a servant to a master rather than as a beloved son to a loving Father.</p>
						<p class="mt-3 text-base text-stone-500 max-w-xl">Jesus said, "No one comes to the Father except through me." The destination was never merely forgiveness or heaven. The destination has always been our Father — and His heart.</p>
						<div class="mt-8">
							<a href="https://fathersheartbible.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-md bg-red px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-red-deep">Visit FathersHeartBible.com →</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="hidden lg:grid grid-cols-3 gap-3" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="zoom-in">
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-deep aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-soft aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-deep aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-muted aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-soft aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-deep aspect-square"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ABOUT -->
		<section class="bg-stone-100 py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">About</p>
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-ink-soft mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">The Father's Heart Bible™</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">The Father's Heart Bible™ is a new interpretive English translation that faithfully renders the original Hebrew, Aramaic, and Greek texts while clearly revealing God's identity as our Father — and His heart toward His children — throughout Scripture. It fills a gap no other translation addresses.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- BEYOND NAME TO HEART -->
		<section class="bg-stone-50 py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center mb-12">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">Distinctive</p>
					<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-ink-soft sm:text-4xl" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Beyond Name to Heart</h2>
					<p class="mt-4 text-stone-600 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">The Father's Heart Bible doesn't merely reveal the Father's name — it reveals His heart. A Father who:</p>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
					{['Pursues His children with relentless love.', 'Delights in them with singing and joy.', 'Grieves when they wander.', 'Runs to embrace them when they return.', 'Invites them home with arms wide open.'].map((item, i) => (
						<div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-200 text-center" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay={String((i % 4) + 1)}>
							<div class="flex h-10 w-10 mx-auto items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-wash text-red mb-3">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12Z" /></svg>
							</div>
							<p class="text-stone-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
				<p class="mt-10 text-center font-serif text-xl font-bold text-ink-soft leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up">
					One message for every reader:<br />
					<span class="text-red">"Come home. You belong to Me. You are My beloved child."</span>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="bg-red px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl mb-4" data-animate="fade-up">Place His Word in the Nations</h2>
				<p class="text-stone-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Each gift of $100 places three Father's Heart Bibles into the hands of readers worldwide — empowering them to hear their Father's voice for the first time.</p>
				<a href="https://fathersheartbible.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-stone-50 text-red font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-md hover:bg-red-wash transition-colors" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">FathersHeartBible.com →</a>
				<p class="mt-6 text-stone-300 text-sm" data-animate="fade-in" data-delay="3">Published by Spirit Media.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
